### NFSIM-EOG-01 — EOG Glasses

**README.** Electrooculography glasses for eye movement tracking. Sleep stage detection (REM), gaze-based BCI.

**SPECIFICATIONS.** ADS1299 4-channel + periorbital dry electrodes built into glasses temples and bridge; BLE; ~$88.

**THEORY.** Electrical potential difference between cornea and retina rotates with eye movement; EOG measures this.

**ASSEMBLY.** Standard glasses frame with electrodes integrated into temples and bridge.
